ycloserine, Ethambutol, Pyridoxine, Ethionamide, Pretomanid, Aminosalicylic acid', 'Diamorphine, Acamprosate, Lofexidine, Naltrexone, Varenicline, Disulfiram, Nalmefene, Nicotine', 1767369485);
